'''The Spacer Quarter''' was a section of the city of [[Aldera/Legends|Aldera]] that catered to the needs of offworlders. Services offered included several bars, a gambling hall, several hotels, a public park, and a pawnbroker. [[Ahr's Dive]], the [[Drunken Thranta]], the [[Eclipse (bar)|Eclipse]], the [[Tranquility (bar)|Tranquility]], and [[Spacer's Luck]] were located in the Spacer Quarter. [[Hotel Stopover]] and [[Hotel Low-Orbit]] were also located in the Quarter.<ref name="CatCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

